metadata.name: Confuse(de) (il)Lusions #01
metadata.description:
Confuse(de) (ill)usions is a series of digital images by Max Fowler.  
A celebratory act of collaborative experiments investigating the possibilities and limitations of using AI as collaborator.  Employing a selection of mixed media collage work created between 2020-2022 to generate image variables to then be curated . The pieces minted on the  contract exist to represent my working relationship as an artist using the OpenAI platform as collaborator and medium between the months of July to October 2022.
